{
  "stem": "11611.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We didn't have an office anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't have a library, we didn't have secretaries, and I didn't understand government finance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had a pretty good budget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't have the slightest idea of how it worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't understand the main function of my job, which was public relations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't like public relations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- I would have two groups of people outside the government descending on me, Jewish groups who said how come you haven't hung anybody lately, or hanged them?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, where have you've been?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I'd get the groups like Baltics, Ukrainians who said how come you're persecuting our-- our co-nationals?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't stand really either group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had more sympathy to the Jewish groups, but they were haranguing me to produce some quick executions, and I knew I wasn't going to wind up producing some quick executions.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought that in various ways my designated deputy was attempting to undermine me while I was trying to carry on this goddamn job and I became quite incensed about that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it all became very troublesome because the unnamed deputy was busy cultivating congressional figures that were important to this program, like Liz Holtzman, who was a supporter of his.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was busy dealing with somebody like Simon Wiesenthal, with whom he was close.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would talk to him occasionally and said, you know, I'd like to meet with Wiesenthal and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He never intimated that he knew anything about Wiesenthal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I finally dealt with Wiesenthal directly and formed my own opinion of his operations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I decided there was one thing I was going to do when I was in office and that was bring cases.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
